---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro"
---

<Layout title="About Us | Free Resume Builder" description="Learn about ResumeBuilder - our mission to help professionals create standout resumes for free.">
  <section style="padding:6rem 2rem 0;min-height:auto;display:block;max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center">
    <div class="hero-split-content" style="max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center">
      <span class="eyebrow">About Us</span>
      <h1>Making Professional <span class="gradient-text">Resume Tools</span> Accessible to Everyone</h1>
      <p>Our mission is to remove barriers between talented professionals and their dream jobs with free, ATS-friendly resume tools.</p>
      <div class="hero-split-actions" style="justify-content:center">
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Build My Resume</a>
        <a href="/resume-examples" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">View Examples</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <article>
        <p>ResumeBuilder is a free, online resume creation tool designed to help job seekers build professional, ATS-friendly resumes quickly and easily. Our mission is to remove barriers between talented professionals and their dream jobs.</p>

        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p>ResumeBuilder was created to solve a simple problem we experienced firsthand: existing resume builders were either too expensive, too complicated, or produced resumes that Applicant Tracking Systems couldn't read. After helping friends and family rewrite their resumes for job applications, we realized how broken the system was. Premium tools charged $20-30/month for basic features, while free options either watermarked your work or locked PDF export behind a paywall. Worst of all, most produced resumes that ATS systems couldn't parse correctly, meaning qualified candidates were being filtered out before recruiters ever saw their applications.</p>

        <p>We built ResumeBuilder to be the tool we wished had existed during our own job searches — completely free, genuinely useful, and engineered for ATS compatibility from day one. Every feature was designed with one question in mind: "Does this help someone get a job?" Not "Does this drive upgrades?" Not "Can we monetize this?" Just: does it help. That philosophy guides every decision we make, from the templates we design to the AI writing tools we provide.</p>

        <p>Since launching, we've helped thousands of professionals create resumes that actually get results. Our tools are used by everyone from recent graduates applying for their first internships to seasoned executives pursuing C-suite roles. We've seen users land interviews at Google, Amazon, Microsoft, McKinsey, Goldman Sachs, and hundreds of other companies. While we can't take all the credit — our users have the skills and experience — we're proud that our tools helped them present their best selves on paper.</p>

        <p>Our commitment to being free isn't a marketing gimmick. It's core to our mission. We believe that access to professional resume tools shouldn't depend on your budget. Whether you're a student with no income, a career changer investing in a new path, or a professional between jobs, you should have the same quality of tools as someone who can afford a premium subscription. We sustain the platform through optional affiliate partnerships with products we genuinely recommend — nothing that compromises the free experience for our users.</p>

        <h2>How Our Resume Tools Work Together</h2>
        <p>ResumeBuilder isn't just a single tool — it's a complete career toolkit designed to work together seamlessly. Start with our <a href="/">resume builder</a> to create a professional, ATS-optimized resume in minutes. Then run your finished resume through our <a href="/ats-score">ATS Score Checker</a> to identify any keyword gaps or formatting issues before you apply. Generate a matching <a href="/cover-letter">cover letter</a> that complements your resume and tells your story from a different angle. Polish your bullet points with our <a href="/bullet-point-improver">bullet point improver</a> to ensure every achievement hits hard.</p>

        <p>Need help finding the right words for your professional summary? Use our <a href="/resume-summary-generator">summary generator</a> to craft a compelling opening statement. Browse our <a href="/resume-examples">resume examples</a> library featuring 90+ industry-specific templates for inspiration. Check our <a href="/templates">template guide</a> to match your career level with the right design. And when you're ready to write a complete application package, our <a href="/blog">blog</a> has 30+ articles covering everything from ATS optimization to interview preparation.</p>

        <h2>Our Approach to ATS Compatibility</h2>
        <p>Applicant Tracking Systems reject 75-88% of resumes before they reach a recruiter. Most resume builders ignore this reality, focusing only on visual design. We took the opposite approach: every template in our builder is engineered to parse correctly in major ATS platforms including Workday, Taleo, Lever, Greenhouse, iCIMS, and SmartRecruiters. We avoid formatting patterns that confuse parsers — no tables, text boxes, columns, headers/footers with critical content, or embedded graphics. Every template uses standard section headings, clean hierarchies, and semantic structure that ATS systems understand.</p>

        <p>Our ATS Score Checker goes a step further by analyzing your resume against a target job description to identify keyword gaps, formatting issues, and content improvements. It checks for 5 critical dimensions: keyword match rate, formatting compatibility, contact information completeness, section structure, and action verb usage. This isn't a generic score — it's a specific, actionable analysis that tells you exactly what to fix.</p>

        <h2>Privacy & Data Security</h2>
        <p>Your resume contains some of your most sensitive personal information — your name, address, phone number, email, employment history, and educational background. We take the responsibility of handling this data seriously. That's why ResumeBuilder operates entirely in your browser. When you build a resume on our site, your data never leaves your device. We don't store, transmit, or have access to any personal information you enter. Your resume is stored in your browser's localStorage, which means only you can see or access it.</p>

        <p>This client-side architecture means there are no servers to hack, no databases to breach, and no data to sell. We don't require accounts, logins, or email sign-ups to use any of our core tools. The only data we collect is standard anonymous analytics (page views, tool usage patterns) through Google Analytics, which helps us understand how people use our site and what we should improve. You can read our full <a href="/privacy">privacy policy</a> for detailed information.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="container-content">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="features-grid">
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="8" y1="21" x2="16" y2="21"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>100% Free</h3>
            <p>No hidden fees, no credit card required. All templates and features are completely free.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="9 11 12 14 22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h11"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>ATS-Friendly</h3>
            <p>Our templates are optimized for Applicant Tracking Systems, ensuring your resume gets seen by recruiters.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"/><line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Multiple Templates</h3>
            <p>Choose from Classic, Modern, Professional, and Creative designs to match your industry.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="card feature-card-left">
          <div class="card-icon" style="background:var(--primary-light)">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--primary)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Privacy First</h3>
            <p>Your data stays on your device. We never store or share your personal information.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

